North America dominates the quartz countertop market due to strong residential remodeling activity, premium kitchen renovation trends, advanced distribution networks, and high consumer awareness regarding engineered stone products. Continuous innovation in sustainable quartz manufacturing and luxury surface designs further supports regional growth.

